Package layout

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountFragment
    A Fragment class that the user is greeted with after logging in.
    BrowseFragment
    Fragment that displays a recipe summary that has been received by the API from Retrofit within a CardView.
    CalendarFragment
    Fragment that opens within AccountFragment when the user logs in.
    CreateAccountFragment
    A Fragment that handles dealing with creating a new user.
    FilterFragment
    A Fragment that allows the user to change their settings in the database along with the ability to upload a picture using Intent.
    PlanFragment
    A Fragment that handles with updating the plan with the MealList and MealList.Meal that Retrofit returns from the API.
